MDFF comes with several python scripts to manipulate input 
and output files from the main MD code

poszi.py              :  generate plots from OSZIFF (mdff output) file
cartoff.py            :  convert POSCAR (vasp) to POSFF (mdff)
fftocar.py            :  convert POSFF (mdff) to POSCAR (vasp)    
fftoconf.py           :  convert POSFF (mdff) to CONFIG (DLPOLY) 
fftohis.py            :  convert TRAJFF (mdff) to HISTORY (DLPOLY)
forcecp2k.py          :  extract forces from CP2K output
random_struct.py      :  generate random configuration (not general)
xyztoff               :  need to be update as python script
histoff               :  need to be updated as python script

USEFUL 
random_struct+stochio
read_quench_table.py
read_statis
gen_quench_controls


